<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavatsarē vasuviyattigmāṁśusaṁkhyāyutē śuklē kārttikanāgapaṁcchamadinē siṁhyācalādhīśituḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> bhaṁḍḍā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rē varadīpadaṁḍasahitākhaṁḍapradīpāya tāḥ paṁcchāśat pramitā Ajāśca kanakaṁ ḍappābhujaṁggā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hvayaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śūrō dhīraguṇānvitaḥ priyahitassōmāyarā<unclear>vuttu</unclear>kaḥ kastūrāya sudhāya nāraṇapaḍī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rāyīhvaputrōttamakṣēmāyurvvarakīrttipūrttivijayaśrīpuṣṭitējōmahāśauryyau
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dāryyamahat guṇānabhilaṣannācaṁdratāraṁ dadau <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1208 gunēṁṭṭi kārtti
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ka śukla nāgapaṁcchamiyu nnādivāramunāṁḍu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sannidhini nityamu nakhaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍadīpamu Ettuṭakunu kasturādhāyinārāyaṇapaḍirāyani putruṁḍu ḍappābhujaṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>gu ssōmāyirāvuttu tanaku nāyurārōgyaiśva<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>yyābhivṛddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyanā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>thuni bhaṁḍāramuna dīpadaṁḍamunnu Eṁbhayi goṟiyalaṁ beṭṭi Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nu dhārāpūrvvakamu sēsi Icche Ī dha<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmuvu śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

